Part/Clause Affected by the Issue: 10303-1114:2004 (Classification assignment) 5.2.2.1
Other Parts Affected by the Issue: 10303-54, 10303-1289, 10303-1293, 10303-1351, 10303-1111
Problem Description:
Entity applied_classification_assignment is declared in this standard and also in ISO/DIS 10303-54
